WEBVTT

00:01.167 --> 00:02.634
<i>NARRATOR: Previously on</i> One Tree Hill.

00:02.702 --> 00:04.101
Here's to hanging with our crew.

00:04.170 --> 00:06.570
And to everyone getting what they want.

00:06.639 --> 00:08.129
I've kind of been seeing my boss.

00:08.208 --> 00:10.938
Alice is considering me for an on-air
position and those are hard to get.

00:11.011 --> 00:12.740
I'm really glad Brooke set us up.

00:12.812 --> 00:14.040
(CELL PHONE VIBRATING)

00:21.321 --> 00:23.619
Haven't you learned
you only get off when I do?

00:23.690 --> 00:26.022
- This is over.
- Then you're fired.

00:26.092 --> 00:29.152
You're just upset because the talent left
your band. Come on.

00:29.229 --> 00:30.218
- Hey.
- Hey, man.

00:30.296 --> 00:32.594
Hey! He's not worth it, okay? Let it go.

00:32.665 --> 00:34.292
- You're lucky.
- Oh!

00:35.568 --> 00:40.096
I'm a little drunk, so in case I said
a lot of inappropriate things tonight,

00:40.173 --> 00:41.470
I meant all of them.

00:41.541 --> 00:43.304
I know Peyton's the reason
you're writing again

00:43.376 --> 00:45.901
and I refuse to be a chapter in that book.

00:45.979 --> 00:46.968
Lindsey, Lindsey, wait.

00:47.047 --> 00:50.539
I fly to LA, I ask you to marry me,
you said no, so I moved on.

00:50.617 --> 00:51.845
Why haven't you?

00:51.918 --> 00:54.216
Because I should have said yes.

